Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.90,0:00:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.53,0:00:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.82,0:00:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not uncommon to see students skipping class\Non the rooftop in manga and such,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.65,0:00:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you actually took a nap up there,\Nyou'd get a sunburn like no other.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I think third period is about\Nto start for everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.61,0:00:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I pretty much always skipped classes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.90,0:00:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and Adachi rarely ever came to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We happened to meet up here by chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.32,0:00:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and ended up spending a lot of time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I serve next?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:00:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.86,0:01:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.11,0:01:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I found out how to do that serve online.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't have a racket at home,\Nso I practiced with a rice paddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No fair using curveballs on amateurs like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You lack ambition, young Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.11,0:01:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's not my... fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.49,0:01:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,When we're skipping class like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,--we can usually sense if the other is here.\N--I can only get it to work like\None out of ten times right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,--And we usually find each other up here.\N--So you're getting worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.15,0:01:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess third period was PE class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What if they come up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we open the windows and jump?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! But we're on the second floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.44,0:01:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't we break our legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see that you lack calcium in your diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:02:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't like that interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap. This is sorta exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think they realize\Nwe're up here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll just drink some milk\Nwith my lunch today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.07,0:02:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So my legs don't break if we ever have to jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you've decided\Nto strengthen your bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This time we spent together\Nwhere nothing else mattered
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,always felt so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shukoh... Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I can't anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost lunchtime anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My, how lewd. Our school's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dignity?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that! Our school's dignity\Nis at stake here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lunchtime, but what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:05:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. We can't have you\Ngo out in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I always seem to have\Ndifferent opinions about "next time."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you probably want your usual danish,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but do you want milk today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Water, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing bad things with Adachi is pretty fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because I got hooked\Ndoing this with Adachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,or do I just get a rush doing bad things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer's obvious, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave things ambiguous for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she even doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura was the first one to be up here\Non the second floor of the gymnasium.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She still looked like a middle schooler,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so I figured she was a first-year like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Adachi, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, we're in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My nickname's Shimamura, but in hiragana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I just happened to stop by today.\NWhat about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you able to touch them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Cicadas aren't too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Think it'll stay on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How many days do you think it has left?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer do you want it to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen days... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen days later,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura's hands were covered in dirt\Nwhen she came up to the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my first encounter with Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you the last danish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This was still when
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't consider Shimamura my friend yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Tea"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Squeak, squeak, squeak, squeak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pshuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Learning Table Tennis From Zero"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess they have a book for everything.\NDang, that's expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha lookin' at?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,--Smash! You joining the table\Ntennis club, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hino is a classmate\Nwho's sort of a plain jane.\N--Smash! You joining the table\Ntennis club, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hino is a classmate\Nwho's sort of a plain jane.\N--No, I was just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,--She's never even dyed her hair before.\N--No, I was just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,--She's never even shoplifted, either.\N--Curious? You randomly picked\Na book about ping-pong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,--She's apparently never pulled the hair\Nof a girl from another school, either.\N--Curious? You randomly picked\Na book about ping-pong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,--Jeez. You just leave me behind\Nand end up finding Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,--My other classmate, Nagafuji, is your\Nusual bespectacled girl with big boobs.\N--Jeez. You just leave me behind\Nand end up finding Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,--Need I say more?\N--Jeez. You just leave me behind\Nand end up finding Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,--Need I say more?\N--So, what were you\Ntalking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,--Her big boobs and her big attitude\Nmake her pretty mature...\N--Nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,--All right. I won't inquire any further then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,--...but she's a bit dumb.\N--All right. I won't inquire any further then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hino, do you have an excuse\Nfor that blatant sexual harassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagafuji is too self-conscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought I'd lighten the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when they're this big,\Nthe boys always look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'm self-conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure all the boys in class\Nstaring at your boobies
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,have fondled them at least\Nten times in their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! That's gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the price you pay for being famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, whoops. My hand slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, Hino and Nagafuji\Nhave been friends since they were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I became friends with them\Nafter we got into high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so my distance with them varies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But when it comes to distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,being as close as you can be\Nisn't always the best option.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get too close, you might fight\Nand have misunderstandings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. The other day at the fishing hole\Nthere was someone in a spacesuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I think relationships with others
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,are like free diving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who was that?\NWasn't she in our class in like April?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that like every time we see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She's our classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She's definitely a certified delinquent.\NTeacher-approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she one of yours, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep sinking deeper and deeper,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and things start disappearing around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You struggle to breathe, so you try\Nto get back to the water's surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you poke your head out\Nfor a breath of air
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,before sinking deeper yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep repeating that cycle...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're late today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...thought I'd just head home,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but I heard the sound of a ping-pong ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your school bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In my bicycle's basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm heading home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:12:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Let's go to class today,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,or "Let's walk home together today."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Which would you prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.11,0:13:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case... I'll just go kill some time\Nsomewhere until school's over... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to be sitting\Nthe same exact way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it started raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the rain's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way is your house, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I just figured your house\Nwas pretty far from mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I live this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, whose home\Nshould we go home to first?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a novel way of putting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... Why don't we go to your place first?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Riding a bike like this is a crime, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that matters. We're delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, being delinquents rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess you actually have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean Hino and Nagafuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were always up there\Nbecause you didn't have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably my only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing time outside of school\Nand then going home together is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is definitely weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but the idea sounded amusing and elating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If either of us were actually\Nhonor students, we'd say,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"We shouldn't be doing this!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And try to steer the other back down\Nthe right path with the power of friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but we were both pretty irresponsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So we were just dragging\Neach other down deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So I go through here, and then...\Nto get back to my house...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty decent walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I got you a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wh-Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad for making you take\Na really long way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to give you a ride home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No. This whole ride\Nwould be pointless, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll probably see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When I looked down at Adachi's head\Nfrom the back of her bicycle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed her hair that usually\Nlooked so pretty with her face
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,also looked like some floofy creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I looked the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What a weird day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I told you there were noises\Ncoming from upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I guess you really were\Nplaying table tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Gack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really say, "Gack" to your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how'd you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You were looking at the table tennis\Nbook at the bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoopsie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So... Is that Adachi over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I think that's pretty\Nself-explanatory, but yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys were friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then yesterday... Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nagafuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagafuji and Hino... Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I bought us some bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised they never found\Nyou guys during PE class.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We stayed pretty quiet\Nwhenever there was class.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one do you want, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take whichever one you like, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... In that case... Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you free on Sunday, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This week? I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then wanna go to the fishing hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid in the spacesuit\NI was telling you about is a riot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you basically just asking me\Nto go fishing with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. That's just a bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they wanted to meet you\Nwhen I mentioned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just take Nagafuji with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I have club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're going to the fishing hole on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The next day, Adachi didn't come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a lot\NI didn't know about Adachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and that frustrated me at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What I did know was what I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,After seeing Hino and Nagafuji having\Na blast up here yesterday, I realized again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.07,0:19:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi might not show up again for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was super unlucky, I may not\Nsee her again until graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That was totally possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess my luck does suck. Welp...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Blammo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was planning to stop\Nbut didn't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure I heard you say, "Blammo."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, your house isn't this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:19:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:20:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Eggy Bread"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to give them\Nto you during lunch today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.82,0:20:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so this is "next time."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you weren't going home\Nwith your other friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have been able\Nto give them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.15,0:20:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi had said that I was her only friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's all there is to it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This was about all I could ask
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.74,0:20:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and this was all Adachi\Nwas able to say right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You are walking me all the way home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was my intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me! I'm a plane! Vroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The slight elation that I felt\Nhad given me wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how many steps it'll take\Nbefore embarrassment sets in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.19,0:22:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's Adachi like?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she like? Um, normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That explains nothing,\Nmy dear Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how much I should tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi likes water\Nand usually drinks mineral water.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.53,0:23:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't seem to care about brands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.24,0:23:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So Adachi is a Namekian.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.86,0:23:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen her regrow\Nany limbs yet, though. Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.61,0:23:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything biting?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.86,0:23:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shukoh... Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.44,0:23:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The spacesuit was so white that it just\Ncompounded their awkward presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, a small astronaut stood before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 1: Playing Ping-Pong in Our Uniforms"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, a small astronaut stood before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.57,0:23:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 1: Playing Ping-Pong in Our Uniforms"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.86,0:23:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Adachi Question'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.86,0:23:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashimapedia: Ping-Pong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.44,0:23:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Adachi Question'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.44,0:23:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain the difference between\Ntable tennis and ping-pong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Adachi Question'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're playing seriously,\Nit's table tennis. Ping-pong is just for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.61,0:23:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,--But what about when you play\Nping-pong seriously?\N--Then it's table tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.65,0:24:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,--But what about table tennis for fun?\N--Then it's just ping-pong!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.82,0:24:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,--Ping-pong is but table tennis.\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.90,0:24:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to sound philosophical.
